{"id":469850,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Corey_Beaulieu","text":"Corey Beaulieu (born November 22, 1983) is an American heavy metal guitarist. He is currently Trivium's lead guitarist. He joined Trivium in 2005, along with the current bassist Paolo Gregoletto. He says Slayer, Malmsteen, Megadeth and Metallica are among his main inspirations. He also says Guns N' Roses got him into music.\nWith Trivium.\nIn July 2014, after Nick Augusto left Trivium, Beaulieu said the split \"had to happen\". He also said \"It just wasn't working out\".","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Americans","surface_form":"American","offset":46},{"uri":"Heavy_metal_music","surface_form":"heavy metal","offset":55},{"uri":"Guitarist","surface_form":"guitarist","offset":67},{"uri":"Trivium_(band)","surface_form":"Trivium","offset":94},{"uri":"Lead_guitarist","surface_form":"lead guitarist","offset":104},{"uri":"Bassist","surface_form":"bassist","offset":170},{"uri":"Paolo_Gregoletto","surface_form":"Paolo Gregoletto","offset":178},{"uri":"Slayer","surface_form":"Slayer","offset":204},{"uri":"Malmsteen","surface_form":"Malmsteen","offset":212},{"uri":"Megadeth","surface_form":"Megadeth","offset":223},{"uri":"Metallica","surface_form":"Metallica","offset":236},{"uri":"Inspiration","surface_form":"inspiration","offset":265},{"uri":"Guns_N%27_Roses","surface_form":"Guns N' Roses","offset":292},{"uri":"Music","surface_form":"music","offset":319},{"uri":"Nick_Augusto","surface_form":"Nick Augusto","offset":360},{"uri":"Trivium_(band)","surface_form":"Trivium","offset":378}]}